Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.18,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 他会打死我的-- 我说了,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's gonna beat the shit outta me. I said, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.23,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我要挨一顿皮带了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm gonna get the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.35,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:21.77,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我来挨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.32,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,回你房间去,别出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just go to your room, and stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:44.63,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,(得克萨斯州奥斯汀,1983年)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:02.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,(J米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:10.32,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我30分钟后要回去巡逻-有话快说,出什么事了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm back on patrol in 30 minutes. So, talk fast. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.03,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你已经知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.16,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,可我想听你亲口说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, well, I wanna hear it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.41,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我从一个孩子那里买大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was buying pot from this other kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:22.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他想敲诈我,我们打了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He tried to rip me off,-and we got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:27.05,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 你打算这么说?好吧-- 我说的是实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's what you're going with? - Okay.-- I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.50,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不,这不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:31.47,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我觉得买毒品的是汤米,不是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think Tommy-was buying the drugs, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你只是恰好路过-看到他被敲诈,就动手打人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think you happened to walk by,-saw what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.76,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 汤米没有...-- 乔尔,我问过你打的那小子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- and started punching.-- Tommy didn't do anyth--I talked to the kid you beat up, Joel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:40.60,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还有被叫到现场的警察,我不是傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and the officers-who got called to the scene. I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.85,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,假如你和汤米不是我儿子-你们现在都得进少管所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And if you and Tommy weren't my sons,-you'd both be in juvie right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.40,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你不会伤害他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're not gonna hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:27.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我偷糖果的事情吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Did I ever tell you-about that time I stole a candy bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,那年我十岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你爷爷发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Grandpa found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.78,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,让我把糖还回去-还让我跟收银员道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}made me give it back,-made me apologize to the cashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.74,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,然后我们回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And then, we went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,就在我下车之前,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just before I got out of the car,-man, he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.46,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他打碎了我的下巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He broke my jaw.-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.96,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,到处都是血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There was blood everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.09,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你奶奶以为我死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Grandma thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:56.93,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我的嘴被钢丝固定了两个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My mouth was wired shut for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.97,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,弄得人尽皆知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Everybody knew why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.52,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,丢死人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-It was humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.64,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,既然你知道那种感觉-为什么还打我们?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you know what it feels like, then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.23,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我告诉你这个故事不是为了同情你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not why I'm telling you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:14.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没错,我打过你,也打过汤米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, yeah, I've hit you. And I've hit Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.32,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,但从来没有那么狠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But never like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.66,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,差得远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.70,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,也许我太过分了,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I mean, maybe I go too far, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.58,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我不知道,我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.92,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.80,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,但我比我父亲稍好一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I'm doing a little better-than my father did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.81,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,将来你做父亲的时候...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you know, when it's your turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:49.06,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,希望你能比我稍好一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I hope you do a little better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:28.16,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,最后生还者第二季 第6集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:50.10,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 新来的-- 我来这里两个月了,塞斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The new guy. Been here two months, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.94,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,那就是新来的,有东西要给我吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Like I said. Got somethin' for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.44,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll be fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.78,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我的孙辈们会喜欢的-你怎么找到的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My grandkids are gonna love these.How'd you find 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.41,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我搜了霍贝克那边的老房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Searched the old homes out by Hoback.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.50,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我早就搜过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I searched those homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我知道去哪里找-因为我是走私贩,而你是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I know where to look-'cause I'm a smuggler, and you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.92,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我以前不干这一行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wasn't always this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:25.51,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我以前是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.76,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,密尔沃基警察局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Milwaukee PD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:36.27,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,交易就是交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, a trade's a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.44,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们可以准备好你要的东西-交货日是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can make what you want-and have it to you by
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.07,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 周五之前-- 不,我明天就要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Friday. No, I need it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.37,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,香草味还是巧克力味?-说香草吧,简单点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Vanilla or chocolate?-Say vanilla, it's easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.08,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,香草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.66,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我还要一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, I need one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.71,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,别紧张,你有很多呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Relax. You got a lot of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:27.76,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,乔尔!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Joel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.64,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了?-- 你从哪冒出来的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- What happened?-- Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.98,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 止痛药,她会好的,来吧-- 止痛药?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Painkillers, she's alright.-Come on.- Painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,别动,别碰它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, no, no, leave it.-Leave it, don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.27,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,汤米,怎么回事?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tommy, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.73,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,她做伙食杂务的时候烫伤了手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She was working KP and she burned her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.94,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,怎么烫的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.91,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 我把手臂贴到锅上了-- 你是故意的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I pushed it right up against a pot. You did this on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.37,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我心想“来吧”,然后就行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was like, "Here we go,"-and then I fucking went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,什么?为什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- What? Why?--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.16,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没人看见,当时就我一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No one saw. I was on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.96,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,烫完之后-它变得红肿软塌,可恶心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I took it off and it was all red-and melting and gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.59,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你知道有一股什么味儿吗?猪肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know what it smelled like?-Pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.30,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 谁允许她这么干的?-- 什么叫“允许”?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Who let this happen?-- What do you mean, "let"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.51,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,谁能想到会这样?我当时在吃晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Who saw this comin'?-I was eating my damn dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.26,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 好痛-- 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Oh, it hurts.-- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.68,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,放松点,小宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Easy, baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.10,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 放松-- V医生赶去诊所了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Easy, easy.-- Dr. V ran over to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.31,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他会再带一针过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's gonna come by here with another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.43,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:25.02,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我真的很想再穿短袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just really wanted to wear-short sleeves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:29.36,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,对不起,真对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.41,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没关系,你没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's okay. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.53,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 该死的,赛斯-- 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Goddammit, Seth.-- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.71,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,“15岁生日快乐,伊莱”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Happy 15th Birthday, Eli."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.30,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,希望赛斯的烘焙水平比他拼写水平高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, let's hope Seth-bakes better than he spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.22,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,确实挺高的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.30,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,真好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.81,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:47.94,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你等着,我还有东西要给你-闭上眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Stay right there. I got somethin' else for you.-Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.65,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,别睁开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Keep 'em closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.91,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,好了,转过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, turn toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.58,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And, open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.92,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么?-- 有人管这个叫吉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- What's this?-- Some folks call this a "gee-tar."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.05,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我借了你的一幅画来寻找灵感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I borrowed one of your drawings-for inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.18,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我花时间修过了,这是真骨琴桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Took a bit of restorin'.-Real bone saddle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:20.81,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我给整把琴上了漆,还用电磨雕了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Lacquered the whole body-and used a Dremel to carve the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.56,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,就是那种旋转的小钻机-换个头还能当锯子用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, that's a rotary drill.-Or could be a saw, dependin' on the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.73,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,挺万能的一种工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But, actually,-it's a pretty versatile tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.48,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,总之...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.74,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我答应过要教你的,所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I had promised I would teach you, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.07,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,如果你等会想上课的话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, if you want a lesson later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:40.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,让我听听看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.20,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思?让我弹吗?-- 边弹边唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- What do you mean, play it?-- And sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.71,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不,我不唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No. No, no, no, no.-No, I don't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.67,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,今天是我生日,露一手给我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's my fucking birthday, man.-Let's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:37.46,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}If I ever were to lose you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.63,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}I'd surely lose myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.01,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Everything that I have found dear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:49.06,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}I've not found by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Try and sometimes you'll succeed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.53,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}To make this man of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:02.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}All my stolen, missing parts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}I've no need for anymore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.79,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}I believe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.92,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}And I believe 'cause I can see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.13,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Our future days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.09,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Days of you and me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.48,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.94,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还不赖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that didn't suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.67,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.50,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.80,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,生日快乐,孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Happy birthday, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.86,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,(一年后)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:22.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 是弓箭吗?-- 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Is it a bow and arrow?-- Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.16,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 是水枪吗?-- 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is it water guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.91,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 是恐龙吗?-- 你猜不到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- No.-- Is it a dinosaur! You're not gonna guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.04,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,等等,是一锅小猫吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait. Is it a "lotter" of kittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.25,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,一锅?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A "lotter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你是说一窝吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You mean a litter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.63,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,一窝小猫?真的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A litter of kittens? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.34,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,既是真的,又不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Really. And no.-- Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.42,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,该死,是敞篷车吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is it a convertible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.51,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你要敞篷车干什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The hell are you gonna do-with a convertible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.63,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,开啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Drive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们从这里穿过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We cross here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:52.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这地方的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How do you even know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.23,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,在巡逻时发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I found it on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:59.48,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,杰西16岁就开始巡逻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know, Jesse was 16-when he started going on patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Is that right?--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:04.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,别误会,我喜欢数蔬菜和铲羊粪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't get me wrong. I love counting vegetables-and shoveling sheep shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:08.12,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得我在墙外更有用处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm just saying,-I think I could be more useful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:13.00,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你早晚是要巡逻的-现在就好好享受当小孩的时光吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}outside the wall. You'll get on patrols eventually.You should enjoy being a kid for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,因为到目前为止-童年一直带给我无尽的快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, because childhood-has been such a joy for me so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你四小时前才刚满16岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've been 16 all of four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.42,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,在你完成训练之前-我们不会派你出去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're not sending you out-until you're trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.13,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你需要一种叫做“耐心”的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're gonna need-somethin' called patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.84,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,杰西说如果你愿意,他可以训练我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Jesse said he'd train me if you let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.76,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你们两个之间有什么吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is there somethin'-going on between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.85,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么?-- 你们经常在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Excuse me? You spend a lot of time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.27,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这好笑吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.65,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我看到你看他的眼神了-我看这种东西很准的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I see the way you look at him.-I got a keen eye for these sort of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.36,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 我不信-- 好吧,不关我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- I don't think you do.-- Alright, none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.44,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,但是有人跟你谈过性教育吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But has anyone talked to you-about the birds and the bees?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.70,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你是说鸡巴和阴道吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You mean dicks and vaginas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 天啊-- 这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Jesus.-- I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.79,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,只要你让我接受巡逻训练-我就保证我不会怀孕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I promise you, I won't get pregnant-if you let me train for patrols. Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.50,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 成交?-- 我尽量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.37,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还要走多远啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, how much longer, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.63,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.22,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,天啊,真的是恐龙!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, my God. It is a dinosaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.85,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 乔尔!-- 喜欢吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Joel!-- Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:19.06,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,看来是喜欢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah. Likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.24,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.03,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.28,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.24,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,小心!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.54,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我骑上他妈的恐龙了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm on a motherfucking dinosaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.35,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 乔尔!那里有座博物馆!-- 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Joel, there's a museum!-- Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.59,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你要是不从霸王龙上摔下来-我就带你去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you don't fall off the goddamn T-Rex, I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:59.85,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这太酷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.27,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你知道这个地方多久了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How long have you known about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.40,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,有一阵子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.65,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不说?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, then what the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.57,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我想找个特殊的日子告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I was saving it for a special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.74,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,看吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You see? Patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.45,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 这叫耐心-- 对,我听说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, yeah, I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.73,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,(穿越星空)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还转得动吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It works?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.45,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,一定有人上过油了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Somebody must have greased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你能想象身处太空的感觉吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can you imagine being up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.00,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 你想试试吗?-- 试什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Would you like to?-- Like to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.88,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,上太空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.57,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.28,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,是,那个真的去过太空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's real.That one went up and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.28,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,阿波罗15号,1971年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Apollo 15, 1971.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.59,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,打开看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.73,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.40,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你要上太空了,总要有头盔吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're going up to space. You need a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,选一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.66,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 里面的气味怎么样?--有太空的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How's it smell in there? Like space,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.96,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还有灰尘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.21,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,很好,那你准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, good. Then, you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.41,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,盖不上...停!中止任务!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}People of Discovery, set! Abort!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.54,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,当年他们就坐在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They sat right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.75,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,生日快乐,孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Happy birthday, kiddo.--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.17,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么? -- 这个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's this? This is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.97,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,是我千辛万苦才找到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}something that took-a mighty effort to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.10,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,放来听听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:20.95,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.41,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,很值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It'll be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,“30秒倒计时”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Thirty seconds and counting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.34,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,“宇航员表示一切正常-25秒倒计时”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Astronauts report it feels good.-T-minus 25 seconds.{\i0}
