Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.77,0:32:58.52,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 我去拿外套-- 还有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- I'll grab my coat.-- And a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:14.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,实习巡逻的击杀纪录是多少?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, what's the record for number of kills-on a training run?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.62,0:33:19.21,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,零,这是目前最安全的路径-得从简单的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Zero. This is the safest trail we got.-Gotta start easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:20.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,很好,祝我生日快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Great. Happy birthday to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.92,0:33:23.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,把望远镜拿出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Come on, binoculars.--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.46,0:33:24.98,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,为什么?这里什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why? There's nothing out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.26,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我知道,但这是为了熟悉流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know, but this is about-learnin' the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.13,0:33:30.09,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,假装一下,好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, pretend, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.30,0:33:33.51,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这是规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's part of the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.64,0:33:36.26,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,跟紧你的搭档,搜索郊区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You stick with your partner, scan the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.39,0:33:37.97,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,随时做好一切准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-be ready for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:39.48,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 该死!-- 怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Oh, shit.-- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.19,0:33:43.86,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,有只小松鼠在操一只大松鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's a little squirrel-fucking a big squirrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.73,0:33:46.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,也许应该汇报上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We should probably report that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.53,0:33:50.53,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,好吧,暂时不要搜索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Fine, we'll skip the scannin' for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.91,0:33:56.45,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这感觉挺好的,对吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But this is nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.99,0:33:59.95,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,让我想起了以前-只有咱俩在林间的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Reminds me of the old days,-just you and me on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.91,0:34:02.29,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我知道你有事要忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know you got stuff going on,-but it'd be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.42,0:34:05.46,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,但我们要是能经常这样就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}if we could do-this kind of thing more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.59,0:34:06.88,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,多花点时间相处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Spend time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.17,0:34:11.17,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.80,0:34:17.68,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧?-- 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- You okay?-- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.81,0:34:18.85,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,可你看起来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- It's just, you look...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:20.48,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 不,我只是...-- 你没心事吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} No, I - There's nothin' on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.60,0:34:22.98,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 没有-- “卡什溪,这里是杰克逊”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, nothing.{\i1}Cache Creek, this is Jackson. Come in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.77,0:34:28.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这里是卡什溪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go for Cache Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.23,0:34:29.69,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,“顶峰以北发现感染者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Infected north of Pinnacle
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.82,0:34:32.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,“尤金和亚当需要支援-你们离那里最近”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}{\i1}Eugene and Adam need backup.-You're the closest we've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.53,0:34:36.16,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我十分钟后到,叫他们开始行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll be there in ten.-Tell them to dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:37.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 回杰克逊-- 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Go back to Jackson.-- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.74,0:34:39.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉,这里不安全,快回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie, it's not safe. Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.45,0:34:43.21,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子,乔尔-我是你的搭档,我们不能分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not your fucking kid, Joel.-I'm your partner. We stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.79,0:34:48.80,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:19.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们从这里走下去,比走弯道还快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'll hike down from here.-Faster than the switchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.49,0:35:58.07,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,记得我教你的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You remember what I taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.20,0:35:59.95,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们互为后盾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm your back. You're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.65,0:36:36.78,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:06.47,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,该死,尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oh, shit. Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.27,0:37:08.27,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:14.57,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你被咬了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.57,0:37:20.57,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.08,0:37:26.54,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 还有感染者吗?-- 乔尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Are there any more?-- Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:28.70,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,还有感染者吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are there any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.96,0:37:31.00,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,除了我?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Other than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:35.38,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.09,0:37:43.30,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,好吧,听着,我还能撑一个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, okay. Look. Please, I figure I got about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.30,0:37:45.93,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这样吧,我们回大门口去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, this is what we do.-We go back to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.06,0:37:48.22,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,让他们放盖尔出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They let Gail out,-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.35,0:37:52.81,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,让她跟我保持安全距离,然后我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}keeping her at a safe distance, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.85,0:37:54.86,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,跟她道别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:57.82,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们不能那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.86,0:38:00.53,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,当然能了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.99,0:38:06.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,必须能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- Yes, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.99,0:38:07.99,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你没子弹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.33,0:38:13.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.87,0:38:16.46,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,乔尔,我得回去,我得见见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Joel, I gotta go back. I gotta see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.09,0:38:20.17,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我有事情要告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I got things I gotta tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.76,0:38:23.76,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,有些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.47,0:38:26.60,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 你不明白-- 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}- You don't understand.-- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.47,0:38:30.64,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,- 但规定不让我们那么做-- 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But we have rules, and it can't happen. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.27,0:38:35.69,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,把手伸出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.11,0:38:43.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,把手伸出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.12,0:38:49.70,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,现在慢慢地从一数到十\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, count slowly,-clearly, from one to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.62,0:38:56.83,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,一、二、三、四、五...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}One, two, three,four, five,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.63,0:39:03.01,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,六、七、八、九、十\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}six, seven, eight,nine, ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:07.09,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他还有时间-我们把他绑回去,再把他带回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He has time.-We tie him up and we bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.60,0:39:11.72,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,乔尔,让他见他老婆一面吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Joel, let him see his fucking wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.85,0:39:14.19,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.07,0:39:24.07,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,沿着小路把马牵下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get the horses, bring them down the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:26.36,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我带他往回走,我们在中途汇合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll start walkin' with him,-we'll meet up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.59,0:39:40.67,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.64,0:39:51.93,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,往前走,十英尺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Go ahead, ten feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.18,0:39:54.18,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.59,0:40:24.80,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,虫草菌会让人身上发冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It makes you cold. The Cordyceps.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.51,0:40:28.13,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这我倒是没想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.64,0:40:35.60,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,走哪边?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.15,0:40:40.15,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,右边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Head right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.00,0:41:01.33,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,真美啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:14.18,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,别回头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need you to not turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.22,0:41:18.39,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不,你不能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.You can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.48,0:41:19.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你不能这样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you can't do this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.98,0:41:21.98,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,乔尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.65,0:41:25.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,如果你有什么遗言要对她说-我愿意帮你转达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you have last words for her,-I'll pass them along.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:26.98,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,给她的遗言?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Last words for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.90,0:41:29.07,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不,我要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, no, I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.86,0:41:31.74,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我要听她说话!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need her last words!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.70,0:41:33.91,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,说给我听的!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}For me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:37.87,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我要死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:40.83,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我很害怕,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm terrified. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.59,0:41:47.96,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我不需要看风景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't need a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.30,0:41:52.68,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我需要的是盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I need Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.30,0:41:57.31,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我得看到她的脸,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}To see her face. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.43,0:42:00.94,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,求你让我看着她的脸死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please let that be the last thing I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.52,0:42:07.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,如果你爱一个人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you love someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.99,0:42:12.61,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,你随时可以看到他们的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}you can always see their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.86,0:42:51.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我看见她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:46.42,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.65,0:44:10.77,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我先用无线电通知他们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm gonna radio ahead and let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.94,0:44:14.49,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,等我们到了,我会...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When we get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.78,0:44:19.95,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我会告诉盖尔她需要知道的部分-仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll tell Gail-what she needs to know, and nothin' more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.41,0:44:22.83,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,这么做才对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.62,0:44:27.62,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.13,0:44:33.42,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:18.05,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,我们找到他的时候,他已经被咬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was bit when we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.72,0:45:20.72,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.68,0:45:24.89,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他让我转告你,他爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, he wanted to tell you-that he loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.18,0:45:31.90,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他希望能当面跟你道别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he wished he could say goodbye-to you in person
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.02,0:45:35.44,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,但他不想让你有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but he didn't wanna put you in danger. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.15,0:45:37.40,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他并不害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he wasn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.99,0:45:38.99,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.74,0:45:41.11,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.32,0:45:45.95,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他亲手结束了自己的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he ended it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.34,0:46:00.84,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,不是那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's not what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.22,0:46:07.77,1Z-LZBB,,0,0,0,,他求着要见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He begged to see you.
